title: IASLC WCLC
description:
Access WCLC 2024 Sessions Anytime, Anywhere!

IASLC 2024 World Conference on Lung Cancer (WCLC) is the world's largest international gathering of clinicians, researchers, and scientists in the field of lung cancer and thoracic oncology. Get benefits from wide-ranging and multidisciplinary content consisting of over 300 talks and 1,000+ poster presentations and 18 specialized tracks.

This app is designed for all participants of IASLC WCLC 2024, including attendees, exhibitors, faculty, and sponsors.

Features include: 
- Notifications, updates, and resources
- 24-hour access to all Conference related information
- Access to full scientific program information including abstracts
- Interactive features include Live Q&A
- Connect and network with other delegates
- View Exhibitors' information
- Venue map
- Bookmark and build your schedule
